{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在一个给定形状的棋盘（形状可能是不规则的）上面摆放棋子，棋子没有区别。要求摆放时任意的两个棋子不能放在棋盘中的同一行或者同一列，请编程求解对于给定形状和大小的棋盘，摆放 $k$ 个棋子的所有可行的摆放方案 $C$。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"棋盘问题 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>对于每一组数据，给出一行输出，输出摆放的方案数目$C$（数据保证$C<2^{31}$）。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入含有多组测试数据。<p><p>每组数据的第一行是两个正整数$n, k$，用一个空格隔开，表示了将在一个`n*n`的矩阵内描述棋盘，以及摆放棋子的数目。 $(n ≤ 8 , k ≤ n)$<p><p>当为$-1 -1$时表示输入结束。<p><p>随后的$n$行描述了棋盘的形状：每行有$n$个字符，其中 $#$ 表示棋盘区域，$.$ 表示空白区域（数据保证不出现多余的空白行或者空白列）。<p>","examples":"<input>2 1\n#.\n.#\n4 4\n...#\n..#.\n.#..\n#...\n-1 -1\n</input><output>2\n1\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1217","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}